{"tid":398367,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人講夢想？收皮啦","createTime":"2017-09-13T06:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T07:34:45.000Z","uid":86682,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1a3ab9a58780d1a63b2517b2d4fe0053a55e11","tid":398367,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"去過其他國家 你就會發現<br />\n香港係一個令你抖氣都難既城市<br />\n石屎森林 高樓大廈 全部都係你眼前<br />\n樣樣都係講錢 死讀書<br />\n每個人都為左置業上車<br />\n做撚到狗咁 為既係一個400呎豆腐潤咁細既單位<br />\n由細到大 你可能會曾經有過夢想<br />\n作家 歌手 舞蹈家 運動員 廚師 車手<br />\n到左中學 你仲可以理直氣壯同人講<br />\n你將來要激戰  做張家輝 一個打十個<br />\n衝出香港 但而家 連衝出香港島都好撚辛苦<br />\n每日為左返學 返工 為生活<br />\n已經冇晒時間 冇晒人生樂趣<br />\n賺返黎既錢 只係想儲黎去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見識下井底以外既世界<br />\n <br />\n今時今日你唔會再同人講<br />\n你夢想係成為出色既舞蹈家<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/143558_fbed44e74dfc4690ae1d55f1104c7885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F143558_fbed44e74dfc4690ae1d55f1104c7885.jpg&h=f99bd2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有句說話叫笑貧不笑娼<br />\n而家個社會 連有夢想都會比人笑<br />\n笑你ON99 返多份PT儲錢買樓好過啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n但諗深一層 如果屋企係冇過分既經濟壓力<br />\n點解唔放手一博 去追夢 做自己想做既事?<br />\n他日老撚左等收皮既時候 起碼唔會後悔年輕時冇試過<br />\n香港就係一個咁既地方 將你所有夢想都抹殺 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌!</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我夢想係成為運動員 代表香港去比賽<br />\n雖然人愈大 愈多野要兼顧 揹負愈多責任<br />\n但唔代表夢想就要放棄<br />\n我每日返學 返PT 再練習<br />\n雖然攰撚到叫春 但覺得呢種行為<br />\n只有年輕先可以去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你到老左只會有心無力<br />\n如果甘心老母生完你出黎<br />\n成世做金錢奴隸 我冇撚野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n所以 香港唔會得一個曹星如<br />\n <br />\n利申: 其實個post唔係放負 只係希望所有人唔好放棄自己夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想做就狗衝去做啦 因為人生只能活一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlhRHTBGvjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTlhRHTBGvjs&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=f8bdaff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlhRHTBGvjs</a><br />\n6:58 如果年輕時不冒險,其實是在冒最大的險。<br />\n7:27 如果為了五十年後 我想像中所謂美好生活而放棄現在<br />\n是冒著浪費生命的風險。"},{"pid":"d04e0b33abc987d8164ce582bed68de4e4d913e7","tid":398367,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"成功需父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fde962b5c26bae680129b8645247e4e7211438","tid":398367,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"香港大把有錢人享受𡁵"},{"pid":"c6f961993ae35f0e0eabf26fd809cfc86bb4c987","tid":398367,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功需父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有父幹就唔洗咁頭痕"},{"pid":"c6559462c50f716f2e581cc8b77e16c01c3556d0","tid":398367,"uid":86682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港大把有錢人享受𡁵</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想"},{"pid":"258b2aafb4cb6c2819155abc6a0597dd43b92ef7","tid":398367,"uid":52701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"係香港地，肯同有能力完全付出去追夢真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以自己無夢想或者放棄左夢想都好<br />\n都唔好踐踏其他人既夢想，潑人冷水"},{"pid":"aa929d3449a3a8c41ec6ab7df92b89ffd025e23d","tid":398367,"uid":146642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港地，肯同有能力完全付出去追夢真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以自己無夢想或者放棄左夢想都好<br />\n都唔好踐踏其他人既夢想，潑人冷水</blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  社會病態好撚嚴重 年輕人有夢想 班廢老即刻標籤係廢青 <br />\n<br />\n有樓就傑青，冇樓就廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}